# Full Adder

> [!word] Full Adder
>
> The [[61-Archive/20220318121918-full-adder|Full Adder]] is also a [[61-Archive/20220318121802-combinational-logic|Combinational Logic]] circuit that adds the two bits **A** and **B**, and the incoming carry bit $C_{in}$, it generates the **sum** and **carry** bit as the outputs.

> [!note]
>
> The [[61-Archive/20220318121918-full-adder|Full Adder]] can be used in a cascade of adders, which add 4, 8, 16, 32, etc. binary numbers
